reviews:
This is my latest purchase and got to say it's a fantastic flashlight. Brightness and control is superb and the build quality is one of the best I've ever seen. The switching, the modes etc. are all very well thought out and easy to access. I prefer the side button on flashlights rather than the tactical back button but it's easy to get used to.

Stellar flashlight, highly recommend and will likely buy another couple of them as they're a pleasure to use.

reviews:
This is absofuckinglutely the best flashlight(torch) I have ever seen. I used to have so many flashlights which were made by trashy companies. This definitely worth the price. I am shocked how small it is, and how much heat it will output from the light when you turn on the turbo. You will definitely be shocked if you put your hand in front.

Based on my experiences, I trust the labelled luminosity. So to say, the mid mode with 460lm is about the same light you will get from a $50 trashy light (in continuous use, as they usually dim after several minutes. I brought one of that before this one) or a normal cheap light.

There is no screw or anywhere you can open on this light. You will definitely be pleasant with its build quality. If you are finding one with using time on the first purpose, this is not designed for that for its small size. This is designed to be tactical, easy to carry also.
